</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Althought I am sure everyone is tired of hearing about 'alignments' I think the problems you set forth in this post could be solved through the system of alignments. Newbies would be protected by inhabiting areas rich in their own race. A drow is much less likely to go prey upon halfling newbies just outside rivervale because the land is full of his enemies. Newbies would be relatively safe. To read more follow the link.

<BR>-joe
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
